and saying satanic incantations!

520
01:02:34,157 --> 01:02:36,489
god only knows for how long!

521
01:02:48,338 --> 01:02:49,566
let him go.

522
01:02:51,808 --> 01:02:53,742
an lndian remedy, father.

523
01:02:53,877 --> 01:02:56,437
only our prayers may save her.

524
01:02:57,781 --> 01:02:59,646
but she was...

525
01:03:00,383 --> 01:03:01,611
a miracle!

526
01:03:02,185 --> 01:03:04,881
what happened to your brother?

527
01:03:54,637 --> 01:03:59,074
- a man with the beast?
- the child is incoherent.

528
01:04:20,029 --> 01:04:22,020
yes, the beast is dead.

529
