you're too smart for threats.

546
01:05:32,569 --> 01:05:35,936
do your duty, the king will be grateful.

547
01:05:36,072 --> 01:05:39,064
otherwise, he'll be quite upset.

548
01:05:39,442 --> 01:05:42,843
you have what you need.
l'm counting on you.

549
