beauterne killed a simple wolf.
he is an impostor.

556
01:08:51,434 --> 01:08:53,664
and l am his accomplice.

557
01:08:55,538 --> 01:08:59,269
come, let's drink to our betrayals.

558
01:09:37,013 --> 01:09:38,708
you saw nothing.

559
01:09:59,769 --> 01:10:02,602
you are no longer welcome
at the castle, sir!

560
01:10:02,972 --> 01:10:06,271
tell Mademoiselle de Morangias
that l am here!

561
01:10:06,409 --> 01:10:09,310
- l've already told you--
- speak of the devil!

562
01:10:09,445 --> 01:10:13,074
My son and l were just
talking about you, sir.

563
01:10:13,216 --> 01:10:15,741
lt is your daughter l have come to visit.

564
01:10:15,885 --> 01:10:18,615
- l'm afraid that is impossible.
- l insist.

565
01:10:18,754 --> 01:10:20,915
let him come in, Mother.

566
01:10:24,627 --> 01:10:28,427
be careful, jean-francois,
you know how these matters end.

567
01:10:28,564 --> 01:10:29,724
leave us.

568
01:10:32,969 --> 01:10:36,370
sir, Marianne is suffering.

569
01:10:38,608 --> 01:10:40,235
l don't understand.

570
01:10:43,813 --> 01:10:48,648
however, fronsac,
you are not a stranger to what ails her.

571
01:10:49,152 --> 01:10:50,176
where is she?

572
01:10:53,489 --> 01:10:54,786
follow me.

573
01:10:58,194 --> 01:11:00,321
so kind of you to visit.

574
01:11:00,997 --> 01:11:03,397
Mademoiselle, what ails you?

575
01:11:03,533 --> 01:11:06,331
l am to return to paris,
but that depends on you.

576
01:11:06,469 --> 01:11:08,266
have a safe journey.

577
01:11:12,675 --> 01:11:14,666
l warned you, fronsac.

578
01:11:16,112 --> 01:11:18,478
you have offered me only one present,

579
01:11:18,614 --> 01:11:22,448
and here l give you two
for your collection.

580
01:11:25,488 --> 01:11:28,924
l've been warned about men of your kind.

581
01:11:29,659 --> 01:11:31,422
Men of my kind, mademoiselle,

582
01:11:31,594 --> 01:11:34,995
never condemn people
without having listened to them.

583
01:11:35,131 --> 01:11:38,328
l don't know how this happened,
but let me explain.

584
01:11:38,467 --> 01:11:40,230
you needn't bother.

585
01:11:41,537 --> 01:11:45,473
please, sir, don't make this
more difficult than it already is.

586
01:11:47,677 --> 01:11:51,306
admit that you were not
the man for my sister,

587
01:11:51,447 --> 01:11:54,177
and leave it at that, no regrets.

588
01:11:54,650 --> 01:11:59,383
do you believe that she will remain
your nursemaid all her life?

589
01:12:03,392 --> 01:12:07,590
are you not happy
to leave our province in one piece?

590
01:12:07,730 --> 01:12:11,222
ln other times, l would have you flogged
for looking at her.

591
01:12:12,501 --> 01:12:13,593
times change.

592
01:12:14,337 --> 01:12:18,330
not everywhere, fronsac.
ln any case, not here.

593
01:12:23,279 --> 01:12:24,439
l'm sorry!

594
01:12:25,014 --> 01:12:28,313
will you hit me too
if l tell you to leave?

595
01:12:29,418 --> 01:12:30,612
good-bye.

596
01:12:33,322 --> 01:12:35,790
have no regrets. he didn't deserve you.

597
01:12:38,894 --> 01:12:43,388
on this historix day,
thanks be to sir gregoire de fronsax

598
01:12:43,532 --> 01:12:45,193
ofking's garden,

599
01:12:45,401 --> 01:12:48,336
the beast's end ispartlyhis,

600
01:12:49,905 --> 01:12:53,306
but it is mostly thanks to your Majesty.

601
01:12:53,609 --> 01:12:55,201
let it be known :

602
01:12:56,345 --> 01:13:00,042
ln your sole person
resides sovereign power.

603
01:13:03,586 --> 01:13:06,020
only a beast could ignore it.

604
01:13:06,188 --> 01:13:08,179
that beast is no more.

605
01:13:08,724 --> 01:13:11,386
l have only little merit.

606
01:13:12,128 --> 01:13:16,428
with your power bestowed upon me,
l merely needed to appear,

607
01:13:16,666 --> 01:13:19,726
and the beast laid down its arms.

608
01:13:28,177 --> 01:13:29,701
what is this?

609
01:13:29,845 --> 01:13:33,872
beauterne's carried out his orders,
as we all should.

610
01:13:34,016 --> 01:13:36,007
- what orders?
- Mine.

611
01:13:38,087 --> 01:13:40,749
this is M. Mercier,

612
01:13:41,257 --> 01:13:45,159
special counsel to his Majesty
for domestic matters.

613
01:13:45,728 --> 01:13:49,323
lt was his idea
to send antoine de beauterne.

614
01:13:50,032 --> 01:13:53,092
you're to thank for this prompt victory?

615
01:13:53,235 --> 01:13:56,500
l admire your scruples,
but it's for the greater good.

616
01:13:57,306 --> 01:13:58,637
have you read this?

617
01:14:00,409 --> 01:14:03,503
lt's no longer for sale,
but you may keep it.

618
01:14:04,146 --> 01:14:05,204
lt was banned?

619
01:14:05,348 --> 01:14:07,942
a fable undermining the king.

620
01:14:08,184 --> 01:14:12,416
we'd have had trouble if we waited longer.
people are so gullible.

621
01:14:12,788 --> 01:14:17,316
better to lie than let lies be spread?

622
01:14:18,494 --> 01:14:23,397
truth is a complicated thing.
one must govern with simplicity.

623
01:14:23,933 --> 01:14:26,663
no more beast, no more problem.

624
01:14:26,969 --> 01:14:28,163
lt'll go on killing.

625
01:14:28,304 --> 01:14:31,899
no one will hear of it again.
that's what counts.

626
01:14:32,041 --> 01:14:36,239
l was forgetting.
his Majesty is most thankful.

627
01:14:36,379 --> 01:14:39,143
lt's said you want to go to africa.

628
01:14:39,281 --> 01:14:42,842
ln six months,
a schooner sets sail for senegal.

629
01:14:43,886 --> 01:14:46,946
lf you wish, you'll be aboard.

630
01:14:48,958 --> 01:14:52,587
of course, we'll never speak
of gevaudan again.

631
01:14:54,230 --> 01:14:55,697
well, fronsac?

632
01:18:22,338 --> 01:18:24,238
Marianne de Morangias?

633
01:18:25,107 --> 01:18:28,736
Madame, l don't believe l know you.

634
01:18:30,646 --> 01:18:34,844
we both have a friend in common.

635
01:18:36,518 --> 01:18:38,145
what are you doing here?

636
01:18:38,287 --> 01:18:40,585
lt's useless to hide behind that veil.

637
01:18:41,256 --> 01:18:43,520
your perfume is not that of a lady.

638
01:18:46,295 --> 01:18:49,787
