has only loved one woman.

639
01:18:49,965 --> 01:18:53,196
lt is your name
he calls out in his sleep.

640
01:18:53,702 --> 01:18:57,331
he will soon be leaving on a long journey.

641
01:18:58,440 --> 01:18:59,805
just perfect.

642
01:19:01,644 --> 01:19:06,445
when you see fronsac,
do not tell him anything of our meeting,

643
01:19:06,849 --> 01:19:09,374
or you will lose him forever.

644
01:19:22,164 --> 01:19:24,325
who was that, my child?

645
01:19:25,501 --> 01:19:26,627
no one.

646
01:19:53,295 --> 01:19:56,628
that one, in the hold with the others.

647
01:19:57,533 --> 01:20:01,663
these two, in my cabin.
be careful, they're fragile!

648
01:20:01,804 --> 01:20:03,135
hello, fronsac!

649
01:20:03,539 --> 01:20:04,938
hey, Marquis!

650
01:20:08,143 --> 01:20:09,667
good to see you !

651
01:20:10,479 --> 01:20:12,037
not as good as all that.

652
01:20:12,881 --> 01:20:15,714
two days after you left,
the crimes began again.

653
01:20:15,851 --> 01:20:19,844
the king no longer sends soldiers.
l can't find volunteers for the hunt.

654
01:20:19,988 --> 01:20:23,014
l can't do a thing.
l don't know how to catch it.

655
01:20:23,192 --> 01:20:26,787
frankly, it wasn't entirely
your talents l was thinking of.

656
01:20:26,962 --> 01:20:28,896
Mani found the child.

657
01:20:29,164 --> 01:20:32,656
just one hunt, fronsac!
you'll be back within the month.

658
01:20:32,801 --> 01:20:36,134
lmpossible! the king has forbidden us
from returning.

659
01:20:36,271 --> 01:20:38,739
- the king will not know.
- so you think.

660
01:20:38,874 --> 01:20:42,435
ls the king's peace of mind
worth all these sacrifices?

661
01:20:42,578 --> 01:20:44,910
you won't change my mind.

662
01:20:45,881 --> 01:20:50,477
- do you want to bet?
- the last time we made a bet, you lost!

663
01:20:51,186 --> 01:20:53,416
l would have preferred not to use this,

664
01:20:53,555 --> 01:20:56,285
but, here, it's from Marianne.

665
01:20:56,892 --> 01:20:58,086
and Mani?

666
01:21:02,598 --> 01:21:04,031
My friend!

667
01:21:12,674 --> 01:21:13,902
how are you?

668
01:21:16,912 --> 01:21:21,076
- we're leaving for the hunt, Mani.
- this time, we'll do it your way.

669
01:21:22,184 --> 01:21:24,175
so, my friend, any good news?

670
01:21:25,320 --> 01:21:28,881
best in the world, Marquis.

671
01:21:34,897 --> 01:21:38,025
ln gevaudan, the crimes continued,

672
01:21:38,867 --> 01:21:41,734
but offixially, the beast was dead,

673
01:21:42,471 --> 01:21:46,464
whatreallyhappened
appears in no historybook,

674
01:21:47,242 --> 01:21:49,642
lt was xarefullykept quiet,

675
01:21:53,849 --> 01:21:55,840
ls he welcoming us?

676
01:21:55,984 --> 01:21:57,952
he wants to help us.

677
01:22:01,023 --> 01:22:04,186
go to the castle. l'll meet you there.

678
01:22:34,022 --> 01:22:35,182
what is it?

679
01:22:43,832 --> 01:22:46,232
where do jeanne and pierre roulier live?

680
01:22:46,501 --> 01:22:49,834
go straight on.
lt's the last house in the village.

681
01:23:53,468 --> 01:23:56,596
this is jeanne, my nanny.

682
01:23:59,141 --> 01:24:01,268
pierre, fetch some wine.

683
01:24:15,157 --> 01:24:18,149
l'm being watched.
they might know you're back.

684
01:24:18,327 --> 01:24:20,852
l'll tear you away from your family.

685
01:24:35,444 --> 01:24:38,902
l can't bear my mother, nor jean-francois.

686
01:24:39,181 --> 01:24:40,739
l want to leave.

687
01:24:41,249 --> 01:24:43,444
ln a week, we'll go to paris.

688
01:24:43,585 --> 01:24:44,847
why wait?

689
01:24:45,620 --> 01:24:48,680
the hunt. l promised the Marquis.

690
01:24:48,824 --> 01:24:50,758
you didn't return for me?

691
01:25:18,186 --> 01:25:19,380
look out!

692
01:25:31,500 --> 01:25:34,526
leave! slowly, don't run !

693
01:25:35,404 --> 01:25:37,099
over here! look at me!

694
01:25:37,239 --> 01:25:39,230
come here!

695
01:25:55,590 --> 01:25:56,818
go, Marianne!

696
01:26:37,199 --> 01:26:39,167
what is this? open up!

697
01:26:43,171 --> 01:26:44,103
My god!

698
01:27:28,817 --> 01:27:32,719
tell me, do you really think
we'll find this beast?

699
01:27:32,854 --> 01:27:34,845
we're short of men.

700
01:27:34,956 --> 01:27:37,857
Mani knows what he's doing.
l'm hunting a man.

701
01:27:41,496 --> 01:27:42,554
a man?

702
01:27:43,365 --> 01:27:46,994
the beast is a weapon serving a sick mind.

703
01:27:47,836 --> 01:27:50,464
- wouldn't a killer be secretive?
- right.

704
01:27:50,639 --> 01:27:53,437
the beast's first mystery is its fame.

705
01:27:55,110 --> 01:27:58,944
lts master wants people to talk,
to be afraid and make noise.

706
01:27:59,080 --> 01:28:00,172
how's that?

707
01:28:00,715 --> 01:28:02,307
this book is sold all over.

708
01:28:05,320 --> 01:28:10,223
lt says the beast is punishing
the king's indulgence in philosophers.

709
01:28:11,426 --> 01:28:12,950
who wrote it?

710
01:28:13,128 --> 01:28:16,222
l don't know,
but the beast has a master. l want him.

711
01:28:37,085 --> 01:28:39,815
perhaps your weapon will help...

712
01:28:40,422 --> 01:28:42,287
but only in your hands!

713
01:28:42,991 --> 01:28:44,390
and you, Mani?

714
01:28:45,093 --> 01:28:46,685
which will you choose?

715
01:28:47,128 --> 01:28:49,392
Mani doesn't like firearms.

716
01:28:49,898 --> 01:28:53,800
too much noise and smoke. bad smell.

717
01:29:15,290 --> 01:29:17,884
all will go well, grandfather.

718
01:29:19,794 --> 01:29:22,627
don't worry. we're well prepared.

719
01:31:36,531 --> 01:31:38,590
tell me of the americas.

720
01:31:42,070 --> 01:31:43,662
will you never go back?

721
01:31:45,607 --> 01:31:47,575
not all my memories are fond ones.

722
01:31:48,009 --> 01:31:50,773
and Mani? does he miss his tribe?

723
01:31:51,312 --> 01:31:53,280
his tribe is no more.

724
01:31:53,915 --> 01:31:58,318
before our attack,
the pox had decimated his village.

725
01:31:58,453 --> 01:32:01,149
orders were to execute survivors.

726
01:32:01,289 --> 01:32:04,122
the women, and the children, too.

727
01:32:04,192 --> 01:32:05,716
only Mani escaped.

728
01:32:06,694 --> 01:32:09,891
- how?
- we needed an interpreter.

729
01:32:10,498 --> 01:32:15,299
l was to teach him our language.
then l found him slaying the captain.

730
01:32:15,837 --> 01:32:17,964
why didn't you turn him in?

731
01:32:18,473 --> 01:32:20,805
know how the captain waged battle?

732
01:32:21,609 --> 01:32:25,340
he gave his scouts
infected hospital sheets.

733
01:32:26,214 --> 01:32:30,674
the lroquois bought them.
three weeks later, we'd mop up.

734
01:32:30,819 --> 01:32:34,846
- and that's our war?
- ln any case, that is how we lost.

735
01:32:38,660 --> 01:32:40,184
where did he go?

736
01:32:41,396 --> 01:32:44,126
- to speak to the trees.
- trees?

737
01:32:44,466 --> 01:32:45,797
trees can speak.

738
01:32:48,102 --> 01:32:51,936
the white man cannot listen or see.

739
01:32:52,707 --> 01:32:54,072
see what, Mani?

740
01:33:00,949 --> 01:33:02,348
want to learn?

741
01:33:02,851 --> 01:33:05,684
- what's this?
- an lndian sacrament.

742
01:33:06,187 --> 01:33:08,655
at your own risk, Marquis.

743
01:33:12,460 --> 01:33:15,429
- what's it do?
- depends on the person.

744
01:33:17,599 --> 01:33:20,033
they say they see the invisible.

745
01:33:22,003 --> 01:33:23,095
so, Mani?

746
01:33:23,738 --> 01:33:27,196
the beast is in the forest.
the wolves will help us.

747
01:33:27,342 --> 01:33:28,604
l see no better.

748
01:33:28,743 --> 01:33:32,679
this night we shall dance
the dance of blood.

749
01:33:34,449 --> 01:33:38,317
and the beast shall come to us
with the sun.

750
01:33:39,187 --> 01:33:40,677
lt has no effect on me.

751
01:33:47,061 --> 01:33:50,360
thatnight, mani invoked spirits

752
01:33:50,498 --> 01:33:54,662
in a language
even fronsax xouldn't understand,

753
01:33:54,969 --> 01:33:57,904
and the wolves brought them to the beast,

754
01:37:06,995 --> 01:37:10,226
don't worry, l'll fix this for you.

755
01:38:37,950 --> 01:38:41,943
don't worry, girl. l'll see to you.

756
01:38:42,654 --> 01:38:45,145
l'll take care of you.

757
01:43:30,208 --> 01:43:34,042
thomas is asleep. a close call.

758
01:43:35,247 --> 01:43:37,442
l'm sorry for the lndian.

759
01:43:37,749 --> 01:43:38,977
what is there?

760
01:43:39,418 --> 01:43:42,819
tell me, what manor is this?
